# Implementation Plan - BDS Website Enhancements

The goal is to "develop further" the existing functionality by turning static UI elements into working features and ensuring data persists during the session.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I am assuming we want to keep this a "Frontend-only" prototype for now. I will use `localStorage` to save your data (new posts, edits) so they don't disappear when you refresh the page.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Data Persistence (Local Storage)
**File**: [index.tsx](file:///i:/Website/BDS/index.tsx)
- Initialize `listings` and `news` state from `localStorage` if available.
- Add `useEffect` hooks to save `listings`, `news`, and `bookmarks` (favorites) to `localStorage` whenever they change.

### 2. Advanced Search & Filtering
**File**: [index.tsx](file:///i:/Website/BDS/index.tsx)
- **Component**: Create a `FilterDropdown` component to handle "Price", "Area", and "Location" selections.
- **Logic**: 
    - Implement `priceRange` state (min, max).
    - Implement `areaRange` state (min, max).
    - Implement `location` state (City/District).
    - Update `filteredListings` logic to include these new filters in addition to the text search.
- **UI**: detailed dropdowns for the buttons in the Hero section:
    - "Toàn quốc" -> Select City/Location.
    - "Mức giá" -> Select Price Range (e.g., < 1 Billion, 1-3 Billion, etc.).
    - "Diện tích" -> Select Area Range (e.g., < 30m2, 30-50m2, etc.).

### 3. Favorites / Saved Listings
**File**: [index.tsx](file:///i:/Website/BDS/index.tsx)
- **State**: Add `savedListings` state (array of IDs).
- **UI**:
    - Update [PropertyCard](file:///i:/Website/BDS/index.tsx#1167-1225) heart icon to toggle saved state.
    - Add a new View/Tab in the Profile dropdown (or Header) to "Xem tin đã lưu" (View Saved Listings).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None (Visual/Interactive functionality).

### Manual Verification
1.  **Persistence**:
    - Create a new listing via "Đăng tin".
    - Refresh the page.
    - Verify the new listing is still there.
2.  **Filters**:
    - In Hero section, select "Mức giá" -> "1 - 3 tỷ".
    - Verify only listings within that range appear.
    - Test combinations (e.g., "Hà Nội" + "1 - 3 tỷ").
3.  **Favorites**:
    - Click the Heart icon on a listing.
    - Refresh page.
    - Verify the heart remains red/filled.
